Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:09.01,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}I had lost my way during my journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:17.02,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Only my soul was wandering, while I stood still.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:25.28,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}But right now, I'm walking to a distant place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:33.53,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}That's right, ever since I met you on this road.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:41.96,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}The travellers witnessed the song, the forbidden song,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:52.72,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}And I became attached to it as I heard it alone with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:01:00.81,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}If the world I saw in my dreams exists somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:09.20,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Let's go search for it, beyond the winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:13.37,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Whether it's a freezing dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:17.58,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A dry midday,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:21.75,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A shivering night,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.75,0:01:28.00,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}or the ends of the Earth, let's go and see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:02:01.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, while I was on my way here from Rubinhaigen,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:02.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,it had already become a famous rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:04.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, it's scary, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:08.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That magician near that newly-made detour road, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:10.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.39,0:02:14.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,He summons wolves and commands them as if they were dogs,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.04,0:02:17.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and attacks travelers to collect their blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:18.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.92,0:02:24.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you should seriously be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.13,0:02:27.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a story I heard from someone who's with the church in Rubinhaigen,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:31.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,but two weeks ago, an entire caravan was wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:35.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, scary, how scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.69,0:02:37.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's scary so I'm going to drink more!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.61,0:02:40.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll keep it in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:45.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I pray the magician isn't a woman, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:47.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:49.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're easily deceived by women.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.95,0:02:52.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're also easily seduced, even if it means you'll get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:57.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then, the price of beer has certainly increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:01.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:07.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The Medioh Company must be a huge topic in bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.57,0:03:13.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Men really are foolish creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.91,0:03:16.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for being an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:21.47,Chapter Name Title Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Wolf and Righteous Scale
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.83,0:03:23.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What an insolent city!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:25.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Bars close far too early!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:29.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because this place is under the control of the Church and Rubinhaigen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:31.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,At least they have bars intended for travelers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:36.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean it's a city that's only interested in living humbly and praying to God?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:43.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The Church's sermons about virtues, that put you to sleep, are like this city's greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:46.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what's so fun about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:52.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,After I sell the pepper and load up some new cargo, I'll take you to Rubinhaigen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:03:54.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a large town?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:03:55.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:56.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's larger than Pattsio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more of a city than a town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:04:01.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's lively, and there are a lot of street stalls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:02.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they have apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure about fresh ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:07.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost winter, so it's about the time they preserve them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:10.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Preserve?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:12.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't use salt, you know, they use honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.01,0:04:18.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not just apples, preserved pears in honey are also good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:21.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, in newer areas, they use peaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.75,0:04:23.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Peaches...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:27.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They cut the peaches into thin slices and pack them into a barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:31.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The high-class versions of the product might even have almonds in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:35.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They then pour a lot of honey on top and a bit of ginger at the bottom,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:37.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and then store it for about two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:44.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The sweetness you taste when you put it in your mouth is a sweetness that's almost otherworldly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:48.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The Church prohibits it, though, because of their doctrines-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:51.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're drooling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:56.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not lying, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:58.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying, but
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:05:00.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,generally, only the rich or noble can buy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:02.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Stores don't put them on display often.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:04.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What if they put it on display?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:06.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What would happen if they put it on display?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:09.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A-All right, I'll buy it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:10.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:12.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But only a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:14.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:17.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:18.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:20.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:22.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:26.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go to the inn, get on the wagon, and go to that whatever-company, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:29.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll strike the doors until the master awakens, sell the pepper at a high price,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.15,0:05:31.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and then immediately depart for Rubinhaigen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:33.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:37.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be sold out, so all the more reason to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:40.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a higher chance of it not being sold rather than being sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:43.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Peaches with honey! I can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.97,0:05:45.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:47.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's only if we're lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:50.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:52.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be hard for me to give up the pears as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:06:01.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't taken that priest's story too much to heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:05.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's truly a meeting that God has sent to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:12.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish to impart those words to you as an expression of the devotional feelings that reside in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:17.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I talked a bit too long, so shall we get down to business?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:19.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.51,0:06:23.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What goods did you bring us today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:24.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.37,0:06:26.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Pepper, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:28.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you could tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:30.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:37.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:40.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, it's something I learned after doing this for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:45.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, did you bring a scale?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:51.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.27,0:06:54.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in God.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:01.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, it's quite frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:04.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The demand for pepper has been rising lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:10.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had come a week earlier, I could've bought the pepper cheaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.98,0:07:13.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I've come at a good time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:14.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:17.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let us weigh the pepper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:19.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.38,0:07:24.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll need some paper and ink, so please wait a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:31.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:32.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:34.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just bear with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:45.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Would water be okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.24,0:07:47.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We also have wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:49.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, could I have some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:52.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A simple request.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:02.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The weight comes to 45 units.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:04.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did this pepper come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.24,0:08:06.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ramapata from the the Kingdom of Riedon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:08.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It was imported by the Milone Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:15.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ramapata is known prominently for their spices, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:18.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, there's no mistaking that this certificate is authentic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:25.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, how about one Rumione gold coin for each unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:29.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the market price for Rumione gold coins?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:32.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Would Thoreni silver coins be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:33.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:36.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In Thoreni silver coins...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.17,0:08:39.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be 32 and 5/6 coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:40.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be by my estimation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:50.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go with that price.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:52.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:57.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:08:59.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bit dizzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.92,0:09:02.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:04.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:07.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:10.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A bit, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:12.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be the weariness from your long travels.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.98,0:09:15.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring you some goat milk now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.76,0:09:17.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:23.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, everything seems to be on a slant to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:27.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it all look to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:31.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I would never...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:34.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it isn't, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:37.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:42.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I see something that can't be real!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:53.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I was drinking wine earlier, rather than water.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.89,0:09:56.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:04.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a proverb that says you shouldn't drink more than the cheerful bar master.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:05.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.99,0:10:10.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The secret to a thriving business is to be the sober one in that situation, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:13.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I'm drunk too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:17.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll probably forget all that I've seen and heard here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:21.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I'm drunk, I tend to talk quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:23.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.78,0:10:27.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The money here, the profit you tried to make off me, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.09,0:10:32.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, to buy my trust, you'll give me double the amount of what I was buying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:35.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Double?! T-That's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:40.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, how unfortunate, I'm becoming sober.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:43.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The commodity will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:48.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, money is money, so how about some high-grade armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:50.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:56.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a safe and standard commodity that will guarantee a profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:10:58.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And with this, I can return the money I borrowed immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:01.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a lot of commodities for Rubinhaigen, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:04.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Armor, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:08.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a company that's friendly with me in Rubinhaigen,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:12.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,so the lending and borrowing would counterbalance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:15.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.35,0:11:19.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.04,0:11:22.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, could you make arrangements for the goods now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:25.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to depart for Rubinhaigen as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:28.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I understand. What about the audit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:32.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave it to you. I believe in God after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.40,0:11:45.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:49.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, I'm amazed that you noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:52.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm beautiful, the lay of my tail is good, and I'm smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:54.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But my ears and eyes are good too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:57.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I smelled it right when I entered this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:11:58.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:12:00.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Not "Oh!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:03.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, so suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:05.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Experience leads to trusting others too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:07.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And that trust can sometimes be fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:09.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have learned that after Chloe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:12.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's entirely true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.53,0:12:14.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.74,0:12:16.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling sorry for yourself is even worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:19.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just learn from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:31.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Oil?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.40,0:12:35.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I hear it's good for maintaining my tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:37.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you buy me some in the next city?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.27,0:12:45.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever calculated the price for those clothes you're wearing, your spare clothes, the comb,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.15,0:12:50.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,the expenses for the inn, meals, and the absurd amounts of beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:53.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There's also the poll tax when we enter a city.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:57.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you can't calculate it, right?{he's using horo's dialect here}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.01,0:12:59.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do addition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:02.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But not only addition, I'm also good at subtraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:05.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then add up how much you've spent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:09.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're so wise, you should be able to know the answer to my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:11.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:16.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you will buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.80,0:13:20.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You pride yourself for being clever and wise, but you just lose face when you're drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:23.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not drunk at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:26.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:27.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:30.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:34.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not good to belittle me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:41.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs37}Don't you understand that you gained that unimaginable profit by grasping onto that master's weakness?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:44.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you buy me oil?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.31,0:13:49.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you think you owe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:50.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,140 silver coins!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.98,0:13:53.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand how much that is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:56.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'll just buy you some more unnecessary stuff on top of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:14:01.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Do you really want me to pay you back that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:03.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:08.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you thought that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:10.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What do you-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:11.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:17.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I pay you back, I'll be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:21.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I should just pay you back and return to the North by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:24.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I {\i1}am {\i0}used to being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:33.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't decided when you have to pay me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:36.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you pay me back when we reach the northern forest, it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:38.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:39.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:44.45,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I will be able to pay you back once we reach the northern forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:53.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I was planning to pay you back with interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.36,0:14:58.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the more I can borrow from you, the more profit you'll get.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:14:59.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:02.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Oil, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:03.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:07.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You can forget about my debt, so will you buy me it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:14.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:15.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:31.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather is perfect this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.57,0:15:46.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But you really haggled with him, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:48.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you asking that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:53.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not good to become a merchant that extorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.92,0:15:59.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Rubinhaigen is the best place to sell armor, but there are too many merchants who bring it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.62,0:16:01.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And because of that, the interest rate will naturally lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.97,0:16:04.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So I just haggled with him to get more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:06.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But you bought this much, so you should have a big profit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:12.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we should have enough to buy oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:15.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:20.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But thinking about it, spice is really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:22.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:25.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat me like you. I'm talking about profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:29.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have gotten more spice, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:32.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The price won't be any different in Rubinhaigen or Polson.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:34.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The tariff would cost me so much that I'd be be at a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.54,0:16:37.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should give up on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:43.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could trade spices or something with a higher interest rate, I'd have my own store by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:45.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:49.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, don't jewels and gold sell well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:53.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be much profit with those in Rubinhaigen and its vicinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.71,0:16:56.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:00.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The tariff is too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:05.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,By looking at a few merchants, they get charged a high tariff when they import gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:08.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do any business because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:12.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are a few merchants exempt from it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:15.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a monopoly with the Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:20.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you take gold to the Church there, they'll carve a holy seal for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.02,0:17:23.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The blessed gold then comes with a preposterously high price.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.57,0:17:27.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, for exempting the tariff, they receive donations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:30.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What a splendid relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:34.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why there's a terribly severe punishment for smuggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:39.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you smuggle it, the price will double,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:41.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,but in exchange, it will also be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:44.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why there aren't any idiots who do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:47.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even import gold by hiding it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:50.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The cargo inspection isn't that laid back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:53.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll happen if they find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.04,0:17:56.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,At the worst, they'll sever your dominant arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.46,0:18:00.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just not worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:05.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, your business is doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:07.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You just need to steadily earn money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.07,0:18:09.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.03,0:18:13.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's someone who's trying to waste my steady gain of profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:29.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:34.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like a mercenary band is coming in from the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:36.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Mercenary band?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.04,0:18:36.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:41.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then continuing on this path would be suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.11,0:18:45.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they're like birds of prey and can find their game even faster than I.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:46.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If they think it will make them money,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:49.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll take everything, not even leaving behind the ashes of tree stumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.53,0:18:52.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They have long spears, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:55.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I have memories of trouble with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:59.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What troubles me more is why they've gone out of their way to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:02.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They're like us, they only move if there's something to gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:07.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's no use worrying about it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:11.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's take that new detour road leading to Rubinhaigen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:16.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not afraid of that pagan magician, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:20.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There seems to be a pack of wolves on the road also.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,0:19:22.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They're easier to handle than humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:25.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,At the least, we can talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.36,0:19:28.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll leave the negotiations to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.45,0:19:41.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.02,0:19:43.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of rumors are exceptionally strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:49.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How boring, I'm going to take a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:53.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll still know if wolves come if you're asleep, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.51,0:19:55.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:19:57.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be troublesome if we're surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:19:59.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a worry-wart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:03.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't normally matter if they're awake or asleep, despite what animal it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:06.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that you humans are too defenseless when you sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.44,0:20:09.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not very convincing, since you snore when you sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.94,0:20:11.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't snore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:14.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not that loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:16.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I don't snore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.47,0:20:18.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,All right already.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:20.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I don't snore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:22.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:26.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.57,0:20:30.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the coming negotiations to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.01,0:20:35.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:38.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The type of humans I hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:41.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That magician?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:02.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheep?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.79,0:21:08.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that supposed to be the magician?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.50,0:21:24.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:27.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a kind of ritual for when you meet a shepherd.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.03,0:21:30.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, she doesn't look like the magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.24,0:21:33.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a travelling merchant, Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.51,0:21:35.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my traveling companion, Horo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.39,0:21:42.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,To the shepherd where God had guided us to meet, I hope that you pray for our safe journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.09,0:21:48.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,With pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.79,0:22:19.77,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven apples on the witch's tree
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:25.15,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,With seven seeds to plant inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:30.33,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,In spring time I grew a magic song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.33,0:22:33.07,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Then skipping along,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.07,0:22:35.63,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I sang the song to everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.63,0:22:41.06,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I look at the world through apple eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.06,0:22:46.39,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And cut myself a slice of sunshine pie
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.39,0:22:51.73,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I danced with the peanuts for the flies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.73,0:22:54.36,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Till someone had told me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.36,0:22:57.42,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,To say hello for every good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.42,0:23:02.38,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Saw some sugar stars
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.38,0:23:07.47,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put them in a jar
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.47,0:23:10.04,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.04,0:23:13.48,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.48,0:23:17.34,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little wolf inside a cart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.34,0:23:18.69,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,You say,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.69,0:23:22.98,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And off I go from June to May
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.98,0:23:28.87,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.87,0:23:32.52,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:44.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Wolf and the Shepherd's Lambs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.50,0:23:49.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Wolf and the Shepherd's Lambs
